			<p>When a user is logged out of our platform, their <i>platform activities</i> may have engaged politicians with our Contact Engine service. <i>I</i>Matr stores the information it collects with <i>unique identifiers</i> tied to the browser or <i>device</i> a user is using, or to the <i>platform activity</i> it is performing. This helps for example, to maintain the dashboard preferences and <i>Scope of View</i> settings of all users.</p>
