			</p><p>Our platform also collects the content a user creates, uploads, or receives from others when using our services. This includes things like the hosting or linking of an issue, suggestions for issue categories and sub-categories, links, e-Petitions, Smiles, Pokes, or SoCos, a user may create.</p>
